headline: Elliott Director Nominees Send Letter to Phillips 66 Shareholders
summary: Elliott Investment Management L.P. ("Elliott"), which manages funds that together make it a top-five shareholder in Phillips 66 (NYSE: PSX) (the "Company" or "Phillips"), today issued a letter to shareholders from its four highly qualified nominees – Brian Coffman, Sigmund Cornelius, Michael Heim and Stacy Nieuwoudt – in connection with the Company's 2025 Annual Meeting of Shareholders (the "Annual Meeting") on May 21, 2025.

headline: Phillips 66 (NYSE:PSX) Urges Shareholders To Support Board Nominees And Proposals
summary: Phillips 66 (NYSE:PSX) recently issued a letter to shareholders ahead of its Annual Meeting to address core issues like board nominee qualifications, refining operations, and potential risks of a company breakup. Over the past month, the company's stock rose by 23%, contrasting sharply with the broader market's 1.6% gain during the same timeframe.
